title: San Francisco 49ers
description: The San Francisco 49ers are a professional football team that is part of the National Football League (NFL). Their brand colors are primarily a combination of gold and red shades, with the detailed hex codes: #B3995D (a gold tone), #E0CEA9 (a pale gold shade), #75603D (a darker gold), #AA0000 (a vibrant red), and #680000 (a dark red). These colors are sourced from their official style guide available on Behance.
